  N_QR -->|NOT READY| N_FMT
  N_RT -->|OPERATIONAL| N_OP
  N_RT -->|SIMILARITY| N_SIM
  N_RT -->|STRATEGY| N_STR
  N_RT -->|KPI| N_KPI
  N_OP --> N_OPR
  N_OPR -->|ESCALATE| N_OPE --> N_OPR
